# App shell

This app uses a scroll + fixed-footer shell. **Read [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) at the repo root before changing page layout or slot content.**

## Swappable slots (edit these)

- `public/partials/scroll-content.html` — main scroll area
- `public/partials/fixed-footer.html` — three-button CTA stack

## Do not modify unless fixing shell bugs

- `public/src/shell/` (bootstrap, mountSlots, ctaLayout)
- Shell wrappers in `public/index.html` (`#app-shell`, `#scroll-content`, `#fixed-footer`)
- `public/styles/shell.css`

Game styles and logic: `public/styles/content.css`, `public/src/main.js`, `public/src/dom.js`.
